      "source_kind": "source-snippet",
      "source_repo": "mesos/chronos",
      "status": "candidate-context",
      "text": "Chronos is a replacement for `cron`. It is a distributed and fault-tolerant scheduler that runs on top of [Apache Mesos][mesos] that can be used for job orchestration. It supports custom Mesos executors as well"
